{
  "texts": [
    "We estimate the likelihood based on the performance of the state-of-the-art model, expecting that the higher the performance is, the lower the likelihood.",
    "We subjectively determine their worst-case severity.",
    "We find that among the 17 remaining datasets, only 6 cause hazards that are not benign.",
    "Upon manual inspection of examples of this data, we discovered problems with D17 and D18 (see Appendix B.1).",
    "We exclude them and recommend prioritizing 4 datasets for application-grounded evaluation of explanations in NLP: EvidenceInference v2 with document retrieval (D38), SciFact-Open (D44), ContractNLI (D49), and Indian Legal Documents Corpus (ILDC; D50)."
  ]
}